This package tests the robustness of the Agent side of the RCF Network
Communication Library. The tests open communications with the library,
and check how correctly messages are delivered by the library in different
situations.

API sanity tests are also included which check that the library API returns
errors when inappropriate arguments are passed to it.

<!-- Describe parameters which may be passed to the package -->
@param max_buffer_size - maximum size of the transmission buffer (the value is
